List all MCP server deployments

Usage:
  mcp-runtime server list [flags]

Flags:
  -h, --help               help for list
      --namespace string   Namespace to list servers from
      --team string        Team slug to resolve namespace from via the platform API

Global Flags:
      --debug      Enable debug mode with structured error logging
      --use-kube   Use direct Kubernetes mode with kubectl; requires admin/operator cluster access (admin/dev/test only)
